The paper introduces a large contextual citation graph of academic publications, which involves natural language processing and information retrieval techniques. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Deep Learning (cs.DL), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Social and Information Networks (cs.SI).
